1. *Dečaci* igraju fudbal na terenu. (The boys are playing soccer on the field.)
2. Moji drugari su *dečaci*. (My friends are boys.)
3. Mama je poslala *dečake* da kupe hleb. (Mom sent the boys to buy bread.)
4. Njih dvojica su *dečaci* iz komšiluka. (Those two are boys from the neighborhood.)
5. Učiteljica je pitala *dečake* da odgovore na pitanje. (The teacher asked the boys to answer the question.)
6. *Dečaci* su se vratili iz škole i krenuli da igraju igrice. (The boys came back from school and started playing games.)
7. Videla sam nekoliko *dečaka* kako se igraju u parku. (I saw a few boys playing in the park.)
8. *Dečaci* su bili toliko glasni da sam ih čula iz susedne sobe. (The boys were so loud that I could hear them from the next room.)
9. Mama je bila ponosna kada je saznala da su *dečaci* dobili dobre ocene. (Mom was proud when she found out that the boys got good grades.)
10. *Dečaci* su se tukli na ulici i morao sam da ih razdvojim. (The boys were fighting on the street and I had to separate them.)